using (SqlConnection connection = new SqlConnection(connectionString))\n{\n    string sql = @"\n        IF EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM TableName WHERE ID=@ID)\n            UPDATE TableName SET Name=@Name, ItemID=@ItemID WHERE ID=@ID;\n        ELSE\n            INSERT INTO TableName (ID, Name, ItemID) VALUES (@ID, @Name, @ItemID);";\n\n    using (SqlCommand command = new SqlCommand(sql, connection))\n    {\n        command.Parameters.AddWithValue("@ID", 27);\n        command.Parameters.AddWithValue("@Name", "John Brown");\n        command.Parameters.AddWithValue("@ItemID", 102);\n\n        connection.Open();\n        command.ExecuteNonQuery();\n    }\n}